  m_Name: Trial of Calling
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::QuestDefinition
  QuestId: Trial of Calling
  QuestTitle: Trial of Calling
  QuestObjective: Summon 5 Minions
  QuestDescription: 'A whisper coils through the air like silk drawn across steel.
    "Power is not measured only in what you destroy, but in what answers when you
    call."


    You are asked, politely, to summon five allies to your side. No
    explanation is given for why they are needed. No battle looms nearby.'
  QuestOutcome: "As each creature manifests, you feel it again\u2014that subtle tightening
    in the atmosphere. Approval? Curiosity?\n\nWhatever watches you seems less interested
    in your companions... and more interested in whether they come willingly."
  MaxProgres: 5
